    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Priced for value and ready for its next owner, this vehicle offers an affordable way into dependable transportation for the right buyer. It shows its age and will best suit someone looking for a practical project, spare vehicle, or low-cost daily-use option. A straightforward opportunity to own at a budget-friendly price.",
