    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Honest little car that\u2019s ready for someone who needs simple, affordable wheels without spending a fortune. It\u2019s not a showroom piece, but it\u2019s a solid budget-friendly option with plenty of life left for errands, commuting, or as a handy backup vehicle. If you\u2019re after dependable transportation at a sensible price and appreciate a straightforward sale, this one is well worth a look.",
      "price": 4950.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid project car with great bones and a drivetrain that still delivers the kind of mechanical character enthusiasts look for. Starts, runs, and offers a strong foundation for someone who appreciates analog feel and straightforward serviceability. Shows cosmetic wear and needs attention in areas, but that also means room to sort it your way without paying for someone else\u2019s half-finished vision. A good candidate for a budget driver, weekend tinkering build, or restoration-minded owner looking for an honest platform with plenty of upside. Priced as-is and ready for its next chapter.",
      "price": 7900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
