    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "A scrappy little survivor with plenty of personality, this car has the kind of honest, road-worn character that turns heads for all the right reasons. It\u2019s the perfect candidate for someone who sees possibility where others see age\u2014an ideal budget-friendly commuter, weekend project, or dependable spare to keep on hand. There\u2019s a certain charm here you just can\u2019t fake: a car with stories behind it and more still waiting to be written. If you want something inexpensive, full of character, and ready for its next chapter, this one is worth a look.",
      "price": 5900.0,
