    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Looking for a cheap set of wheels with plenty of potential? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s an honest budget-friendly option for someone who needs basic transport, a project, or a handy spare. It\u2019s being sold in poor condition, so please expect wear and tear and come with realistic expectations\u2014but for the right buyer, there\u2019s still value here. If you\u2019re after something affordable and don\u2019t mind putting in a little work, this could be a great fit.",
